---
// Component Imports
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";
import Head from "../layouts/Head.astro";
import Hero from "../layouts/WorkHero.astro";
import mangesh from "../images/mangesh.png";
import mangeshFull from "../images/mangesh-lg.png";
import Modal from "../components/Modal.astro";
import ButtonIcon from "../components/ButtonIcon.astro";
import { Image, Picture } from "@astrojs/image/components";

const meta = {
  title: "Mangesh Thombare",
  description: "Portfolio website for a game designer.",
};
---

<Page>
  <Head slot="head" {meta} />
  <Hero />
  <main
    id="content-wrapper"
    class="container mx-auto py-6 px-8 md:py-24 md:px-0 lg:py-12 dark:bg-dark-900 dark:text-white"
  >
    <div
      class="container min-h-full space-y-5 my-2 text-left leading-relaxed px-4 lg:px-8"
    >
      <div id="pagination" class="flex flex-wrap space-x-2 items-center">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="hover:transition-all hover:ease hover:text-geraldine-500 hover:duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:border-b-4 focus:border-slate-500"
          tabindex="0">Home</a
        >
        <span class="h-6 w-6 i-mdi:chevron-double-right"></span>
        <a
          href="/work/#content-wrapper"
          class="hover:transition-all hover:ease hover:text-geraldine-500 hover:duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:border-b-4 focus:border-slate-500"
          tabindex="0">Work</a
        >
        <span class="h-6 w-6 i-mdi:chevron-double-right"></span>
        <a
          href="#"
          class="focus:outline-none focus:border-b-4 focus:border-slate-500"
          tabindex="0">Mangesh Thombare</a
        >
      </div>

      <div class="font-display my-6 text-f-xl fw600">
        Mangesh
        <span class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-300">Thombare</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start md:flex-row">
        <div
          class="flex border-2 border-gray-200 flex-shrink-0 shadow-lg my-4 mx-2 md:w-1/2 lg:w-auto dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-geraldine-400 dark:hover:border-geraldine-400"
        >
          <Image
            class="h-auto object-contain w-full dark:filter dark:brightness-75 dark:contrast-125"
            src={mangesh}
            alt="Mangesh Thombare"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-3 mb-8 px-2 md:pl-6">
          <p>
            This was a portfolio website project for a game designer. His
            requirements were a responsive website which showcased his CV,
            embedded videos and documents of his completed projects and lastly a
            contact form.
          </p>

          <ul class="list-inside list-decimal">
            <li>Portfolio website.</li>
            <li>Responsive design.</li>
            <li>Embedded videos and documents.</li>
            <li>Modal for images.</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div>
              <ButtonIcon
                id="modal3-trigger"
                color="bg-cyan-700 hover:bg-cyan-600 dark:bg-cyan-400 dark:hover:bg-cyan-500 cursor-pointer py-3"
                iconClass="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-current i-icon-park-twotone:screenshot-one"
                >Screenshot</ButtonIcon
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="bg-white border rounded-md flex flex-col border-gray-200 shadow-md p-6 gap-4 justify-around sm:flex-row dark:bg-dark-700 dark:border-dark-600"
      >
        <span
          class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 text-geraldine-600 w-10 i-bxs-quote-alt-left md:h-12 md:w-12"
        ></span>

        <div class="space-y-3 px-4 md:px-8">
          <p>
            Akshay designed my portfolio website. The best part about working
            with him was that, I got a site fully customized and tailored to my
            needs. It is easy to navigate and works seamlessly on all platforms
            mobiles, tablets or PCs. When certain changes had to be made, they
            were delivered with precision within 24 hours of request. He has the
            patience to work at your pace every step of the way. You can have a
            fully personalized experience at an affordable price. It has been a
            pleasure working with Akshay.
          </p>

          <p class="text-right fw600">- Mangesh Thombare</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-shrink-0 items-end place-content-end">
          <span
            class="h-10 text-geraldine-600 w-10 i-bxs-quote-alt-right md:h-12 md:w-12"
          ></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Modal triggerId="modal3-trigger" title="Mangesh Thombare">
    <div class="mt-3 grid place-content-center">
      <Picture
        class="dark:filter dark:brightness-75 dark:contrast-125"
        src={mangeshFull}
        alt="Mangesh Thombare Full Image"
        widths={[300, 450, 600]}
        sizes="(max-width: 768px) 300px, (max-width: 1024px) 450px, 600px"
        aspectRatio={1.24}
      />
    </div>
  </Modal>
</Page>
